data.text: @NerdyPharaoh They are all over here. What I don’t understand is why they think they have to bring down al these other people to boost her up. I have hear Selena sing live & I have heard Ariana song live... many levels below my ass.
@memoryinthesun Stans like to fight which is so dumb to me. I think all music should be appreciated and no one should fight because like it’s better to all get along. I’m such a peaceful person lol 😂
@hybibliophiliac I mean love whoever you want more I don’t have a problem with that but to say she’s many levels above Ariana singing wise... I’d have to strongly disagree.
@memoryinthesun I love Selena more because I’ve adored her for years, but I’ve heard Ariana is so talented !
